spond in many different ways to children's emotions. <strong>Please indicate how likely you are to respond in each way <\/strong>to the situation below.<br>\n<br>\nPlease rate how likely you are to respond in each way to your <u><strong>children in general<\/strong><\/u>, not in response to any individual child.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"lresinstruction","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Parents respond in many different ways to children's emotions. Please indicate how likely you are...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u7236\u6bcd\u90fd\u6703\u4ee5\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\u89e3\u8b80\u4e26\u56de\u61c9\u5b69\u5b50\u7684\u60c5\u7dd2\u3002\u8acb\u95b1\u8b80\u6bcf\u4e00\u689d\u9673\u8ff0\uff0c\u7136\u5f8c\u8a55\u50f9\u60a8\u6703\u4ee5\u9019\u7a2e\u65b9\u5f0f\u56de\u61c9\u7684\u6982\u7387\u3002"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"Los padres responden en varias maneras a las emociones de los hijos\/as.\u00a0<strong>Indique en qu\u00e9 medida es probable que responda de cada forma <\/strong>a las situaciones que siguen.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\nPor favor, valore la probabilidad de que responde de cada manera a sus <strong><u>hijos\/as en general<\/u><\/strong>, no en respuesta a un ni\u00f1o en particular."}},"NextChoiceId":9,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID21","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0OCvVTAwj66A9ts","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID210","SecondaryAttribute":"What language(s) does this child speak fluently?\u00a0Select all that apply.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"What language(s) does this child speak fluently?&nbsp;<b><i>Select all that apply.<\/i><\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"clang","QuestionID":"QID210","QuestionType":"SBS","Selector":"SBSMatrix","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none"},"QuestionDescription":"What language(s) does this child speak fluently?\u00a0Select all that apply.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"English"},"2":{"Display":"Spanish"},"3":{"Display":"Chinese"},"4":{"Display":"Not Listed (Specify):","TextEntry":"true"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ES":{"QuestionText":"\u00bfQu\u00e9 idioma(s) habla este ni\u00f1o\/a con fluidez? (Marque todos lo que correspondan)","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Ingl\u00e9s"},"2":{"Display":"Espa\u00f1ol"},"3":{"Display":"Chino"},"4":{"Display":"No aparece en la lista (especifique)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>"},"2":{"Display":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>"}},"AdditionalQuestions":{"1":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Respuesta"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[]},"2":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Respuesta"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[]}},"NumberOfQuestions":2},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u60a8\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u80fd\u6d41\u5229\u5730\u4f7f\u7528\u54ea\u7a2e\u8a9e\u8a00\uff1f\u00a0<b><i>\u8acb\u9078\u64c7\u6240\u6709\u9069\u5408\u7684\u7b54\u6848\u3002<\/i><\/b>","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"\u82f1\u8a9e"},"2":{"Display":"\u897f\u73ed\u7259\u8a9e"},"3":{"Display":"\u4e2d\u6587"},"4":{"Display":"\u672a\u986f\u793a (\u5728\u9019\u88e1\u5217\u51fa)"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}\u00a0<\/strong>"},"2":{"Display":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}\u00a0<\/strong>"}},"AdditionalQuestions":{"1":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"\u7b54\u6848"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}\u00a0<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[]},"2":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"\u7b54\u6848"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}\u00a0<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[]}},"NumberOfQuestions":2}},"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":3,"NumberOfQuestions":2,"AdditionalQuestions":{"1":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Answer"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[],"QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"MultipleAnswer","ChoiceColumnWidthPixels":null,"DataExportTag":"clang#1","QuestionID":"QID210#1","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"English"},"2":{"Display":"Spanish"},"3":{"Display":"Chinese"},"4":{"Display":"Not Listed (Specify):","TextEntry":"true"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"}},"2":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Answer"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[],"QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"MultipleAnswer","ChoiceColumnWidthPixels":null,"DataExportTag":"clang#2","QuestionID":"QID210#2","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"English"},"2":{"Display":"Spanish"},"3":{"Display":"Chinese"},"4":{"Display":"Not Listed (Specify):","TextEntry":"true"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"}}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0OCvVTAwj66A9ts","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID211","SecondaryAttribute":"This section includes descriptions of family routines and traditions. Every family is somewhat di...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p>This section includes descriptions of family routines and traditions. Every family is somewhat different in the types of routines and traditions that they follow. In some families routines and traditions are very important but in other families there is a more casual attitude toward routines and traditions.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p>Think of how your family typically acts during these events. Read the statements and indicate if each statement is <u>not at all true<\/u>, <u>sort of true<\/u>, or <u>very true<\/u> for your family. Select the response that best describes your current family.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nHow true are these statements about your family?&nbsp;<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"frq_intro","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This section includes descriptions of family routines and traditions. Every family is somewhat di...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"<p>\u9019\u4e00\u500b\u90e8\u5206\u5305\u62ec\u5c0d\u5bb6\u5ead\u65e5\u5e38\u6163\u4f8b\u548c\u5bb6\u5ead\u50b3\u7d71\u7684\u63cf\u8ff0\u3002 \u6bcf\u500b\u5bb6\u5ead\u6240\u8a2d\u5b9a\u7684\u65e5\u5e38\u7ba1\u7406\u548c\u50b3\u7d71\u90fd\u6703\u6709\u4e9b\u4e0d\u540c\u3002\u5c0d\u6709\u4e9b\u5bb6\u5ead\u4f86\u8aaa\uff0c\u9019\u4e9b\u6163\u4f8b\u548c\u50b3\u7d71\u975e\u5e38\u91cd\u8981\uff0c\u4f46\u5176\u4ed6\u5bb6\u5ead\u53ef\u80fd\u6703\u6bd4\u8f03\u96a8\u610f\u3002<br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u60f3\u4e00\u60f3\u60a8\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u5728\u9019\u4e9b\u4e0d\u540c\u72c0\u6cc1\u4e0b\u7684\u884c\u70ba\u3002\u8acb\u95b1\u8b80\u4ee5\u4e0b\u7684\u9673\u8ff0\uff0c\u4e26\u6307\u51fa\u6bcf\u4e00\u689d\u9673\u8ff0\u662f\u5426\u5b8c\u5168\u4e0d\u6e96\u78ba\uff0c\u6709\u9ede\u6e96\u78ba\uff0c\u9084\u662f\u975e\u5e38\u6e96\u78ba\u5730\u63cf\u8ff0\u60a8\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u3002\u6bcf\u4e00\u689d\u9673\u8ff0\u63cf\u8ff0\u60a8\u7684\u6e96\u78ba\u7a0b\u5ea6\u5982\u4f55\uff0c\u8acb\u9078\u64c7\u6700\u4f73\u7b54\u6848\u3002<br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u9019\u4e9b\u9673\u8ff0\u63cf\u8ff0\u60a8\u7684\u6e96\u78ba\u7a0b\u5ea6\u5982\u4f55\uff1f\u00a0<\/p>\n"},"ES":{"QuestionText":"<p>Esta secci\u00f3n incluye descripciones de las rutinas y tradiciones familiares. Cada familia es diferente en tipo de rutinas y tradiciones que siguen. En algunas familias las rutinas y tradiciones son muy importantes, pero en otras hay una actitud m\u00e1s informal hacia las rutinas y tradiciones.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n\n<p>Piensa en c\u00f3mo suele actuar su familia durante estos acontecimientos. Lea las afirmaciones e indique si cada una de ellas es nada cierto, m\u00e1s o menos cierto o muy cierto para su familia. Seleccione la respuesta que mejor describe a su familia actual.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00bfHasta qu\u00e9 extremo son ciertas estas frases de su familia?<\/p>\n"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID211"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0OCvVTAwj66A9ts","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID212","SecondaryAttribute":"Think about typical dinner in your home with your family.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Think about typical dinner in your home with your family.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"frq_dinner","QuestionID":"QID212","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Think about typical dinner in your home with your family.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"In our family, dinner time is planned in advance."},"4":{"Display":"Our family regularly eats dinner together."},"5":{"Display":"In our family, we feel it is not important that we eat together."},"6":{"Display":"In our family, everyone is expected to be home for dinner."},"7":{"Display":"In our family at dinner time, everyone has a specific role or job to do."},"8":{"Display":"In our family, dinner time is flexible; people eat whenever they want."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","4","5","6","7","8"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u56de\u60f3\u4e00\u4e0b\u60a8\u548c\u5bb6\u4eba\u5e73\u5e38\u4e00\u8d77\u7528\u9910\u7684\u5834\u666f\u3002","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u7528\u9910\u6642\u9593\u662f\u63d0\u524d\u8a08\u5283\u597d\u7684\u3002"},"4":{"Display":"\u6211\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u7d93\u5e38\u4e00\u8d77\u5403\u665a\u9910\u3002"},"5":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u6211\u5011\u8a8d\u70ba\u4e00\u8d77\u7528\u9910\u4e0d\u592a\u91cd\u8981\u3002"},"6":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u6bcf\u4e00\u500b\u4eba\u61c9\u8a72\u56de\u5bb6\u5403\u665a\u9910\u3002"},"7":{"Display":"\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u5403\u665a\u9910\u6642\uff0c\u6bcf\u4e00\u500b\u4eba\u90fd\u6709\u7279\u5b9a\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\u8981\u505a\u3002"},"8":{"Display":"\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\u6c92\u6709\u4e00\u500b\u7279\u5b9a\u7684\u7528\u9910\u6642\u9593\u3002\u6bcf\u4e00\u500b\u4eba\u809a\u5b50\u7684\u6642\u5019\u5c31\u6703\u5403\u98ef\u3002"}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1<br \/>\n\u5b8c\u5168\u4e0d\u6e96\u78ba<\/div>\n"},"2":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2<br \/>\n\u6709\u9ede\u6e96\u78ba<\/div>\n"},"3":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3<br \/>\n\u975e\u5e38\u6e96\u78ba<\/div>\n"}}},"ES":{"QuestionText":"Piense en una cena t\u00edpica en su casa con su familia","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"En nuestra familia la cena se planea en avance"},"4":{"Display":"Nuestra familia suele cenar junta."},"5":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, creemos que no es importante que comamos juntos."},"6":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, se espera que todos est\u00e9n en casa para cenar."},"7":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, a la hora de cenar, cada uno tiene un papel o un trabajo espec\u00edfico que hacer."},"8":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, la hora de cenar es flexible; la gente come cuando quiere."}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1<br \/>\nNada cierto<\/div>\n"},"2":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2<br \/>\nM\u00e1s o menos cierto<\/div>\n"},"3":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3<br \/>\nMuy cierto<\/div>\n"}}}},"NextChoiceId":9,"NextAnswerId":1,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1<br \/>\nNot at all true<\/div>"},"2":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2<br \/>\nSort of true<\/div>\n"},"3":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3<br \/>\nVery true<\/div>\n"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false}},{"SurveyID":"SV_0OCvVTAwj66A9ts","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID213","SecondaryAttribute":"Think of a typical weekend in your family.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Think of a typical weekend in your family.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"frq_weekends","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Think of a typical weekend in your family.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"In our family, we feel that it is important to spend time together on the weekends."},"9":{"Display":"Our family rarely spends weekends together."},"10":{"Display":"In our family, people pretty much come and go as they please on the weekends."},"12":{"Display":"In our family, there are no assigned jobs to be done on the weekends."},"13":{"Display":"In our family, there is much discussion and planning for the weekend."},"14":{"Display":"In our family, we have set routines and regular events that we all participate in on the weekends."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","9","10","12","13","14"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ES":{"QuestionText":"Piense en un fin de semana t\u00edpico en su familia.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, creemos que es importante pasar tiempo juntos los fines de semana."},"9":{"Display":"Nuestra familia rara vez pasa los fines de semana junta."},"10":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, la gente va y viene a su antojo los fines de semana."},"12":{"Display":"En nuestra familia no hay tareas asignadas para los fines de semana"},"13":{"Display":"En nuestra familia se habla mucho y se se planea todo para el fin de semana."},"14":{"Display":"En nuestra familia, tenemos rutinas establecidas y eventos regulares en los que todos participamos los fines de semana."}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1<br \/>\nNada cierto<\/div>\n"},"2":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2<br \/>\nM\u00e1s o menos cierto<\/div>\n"},"3":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3<br \/>\nMuy cierto<\/div>\n"}}},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u56de\u60f3\u4e00\u4e0b\u60a8\u548c\u5bb6\u4eba\u5e73\u6642\u7684\u9031\u672b\u65e5\u5b50\u3002","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u9031\u672b\u6642\u548c\u5bb6\u4eba\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u975e\u5e38\u91cd\u8981\u3002"},"9":{"Display":"\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u9031\u672b\u7684\u6642\u5019\u5f88\u5c11\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002"},"10":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u9031\u672b\u7684\u6642\u5019\u6bcf\u4e00\u500b\u4eba\u90fd\u6703\u81ea\u7531\u6d3b\u52d5\u3002"},"12":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u6c92\u6709\u4eba\u6709\u8a2d\u5b9a\u7684\u4efb\u52d9\u8981\u5b8c\u6210\u3002"},"13":{"Display":"\u5728\u6211\u5011\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u88e1\uff0c\u9031\u672b\u7684\u6d3