 some task."},"39":{"Display":"Often rushes into new situations."},"40":{"Display":"Gets quite frustrated when prevented from doing something s\/he wants to do."},"41":{"Display":"Becomes upset when loved relatives or friends are getting ready to leave following a visit."},"42":{"Display":"Enjoys activities such as being chased, spun around by the arms, etc."},"43":{"Display":"When angry about something, s\/he tends to stay upset for ten minutes or longer."},"44":{"Display":"Takes a long time in approaching new situations."},"45":{"Display":"Is sometimes shy even around people s\/he has known a long time."},"46":{"Display":"Can wait before entering into new activities if s\/he is asked to."},"47":{"Display":"Gets angry when s\/he can't find something s\/he wants to play with."},"48":{"Display":"Sometimes seems nervous when talking to adults s\/he has just met."},"49":{"Display":"Is slow and unhurried in deciding what to do next."},"50":{"Display":"Changes from being upset to feeling much better within a few minutes."},"51":{"Display":"Prepares for trips and outings by planning things s\/he will need."},"52":{"Display":"Hardly ever laughs out loud during play with other children."},"53":{"Display":"Tends to say the first thing that comes to mind, without stopping to think about it."},"54":{"Display":"Acts shy around new people."},"55":{"Display":"Has trouble sitting still when s\/he is told to (at movies, church, etc.)."},"56":{"Display":"Rarely cries when s\/he hears a sad story."},"57":{"Display":"Sometimes smiles or giggles when playing by her\/himself."},"58":{"Display":"Rarely becomes upset when watching a sad event in a TV show."},"59":{"Display":"If upset, cheers up quickly when s\/he thinks about something else."},"60":{"Display":"Is comfortable asking other children to play."},"61":{"Display":"Rarely gets angry when told s\/he has to go to bed."},"62":{"Display":"When drawing or coloring in a book, shows strong concentration"},"63":{"Display":"Is easy to soothe when s\/he is upset."},"64":{"Display":"Is good at following instructions."},"65":{"Display":"Likes to go high and fast when pushed on a swing."},"66":{"Display":"Sometimes turns away shyly from new acquaintances."},"67":{"Display":"When building or putting something together, becomes very involved in what s\/he is doing, and works for long periods."},"68":{"Display":"Approaches places s\/he has been told are dangerous slowly and cautiously."},"69":{"Display":"Rarely becomes discouraged when s\/he has trouble making something work."},"70":{"Display":"Is very difficult to soothe when s\/he has become upset."},"71":{"Display":"Smiles a lot at people s\/he likes."},"72":{"Display":"Likes rough and rowdy games."},"73":{"Display":"Often laughs out loud in play with other children."},"74":{"Display":"Rarely laughs aloud while watching TV or movie comedies."},"75":{"Display":"Can easily stop an activity when s\/he is told \"no.\""},"76":{"Display":"Is among the last children to try out a new activity."},"77":{"Display":"Is easily distracted when listening to a story."},"78":{"Display":"Gets angry when called in from play before s\/he is ready to quit."},"79":{"Display":"Enjoys riding a tricycle or bicycle fast and recklessly."},"80":{"Display":"Sometimes becomes absorbed in a picture book and looks at it for a long time."}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID172\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}"},"2":{"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1<br \/>Very false<\/div>"},"2":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2<br \/>False<\/div>"},"3":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3<br \/>Neither false nor true<\/div>"},"4":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">4<br \/>True<\/div>"},"5":{"Display":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">5<br \/>Very true<\/div>"}},"QuestionText":"<strong>${q:\/\/QID174\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/strong>","RecodeValues":[],"VariableNaming":[],"AnalyzeChoices":[],"QuestionType":"Matrix