ertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"At the top of the ladder are the people <b>in general&nbsp;<\/b>who are the best off, those who have the most money, most education, and best jobs. At the bottom are the people who are the worst off, those who have the least money, least education, worst jobs, or no job. Please adjust the slider to indicate the rung that best represents where you think you stand on the lader.<br>\n<img style=\"width: 240px; height: 480px;\" src=\"https:\/\/gse.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_bK2zUbwcgGxxk4m\">","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"msss1","QuestionID":"QID88","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":1,"CSSliderMax":10,"GridLines":9,"SnapToGrid":true,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":false,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"At the top of the ladder are the people in general\u00a0who are the best off, those who have the most...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Rung"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"ES":{"QuestionText":"En la parte m\u00e1s alta de la escala se encuentran las personas (que por lo general) etan en mejor situaci\u00f3n, las que tienen m\u00e1s dinero, m\u00e1s educaci\u00f3n y mejores trabajos. En la parte m\u00e1s baja est\u00e1n las personas en peor situaci\u00f3n, las que tienen menos dinero, menos estudios, el peor trabajo o ning\u00fan trabajo. Ajuste el control para indicar el\u00a0nivel que mejor represente su posici\u00f3n en la escala.<img src=\"https:\/\/gse.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_bK2zUbwcgGxxk4m\" style=\"width: 240px; height: 480px;\" \/>","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Nivel"}},"Labels":[]},"ZH-T":{"QuestionText":"\u8acb\u4f7f\u7528\u6ed1\u584a\u4f86\u8868\u793a\u60a8\u8a8d\u70ba\u81ea